name: CompositeMap_containsKeyTest
description: Unit tests for the containsKey method of the CompositeMap class.

test_cases.name: testContainsKey_KeyInFirstMap
test_cases.description: Tests if the CompositeMap contains a key that is present in the first map.

test_cases.name: testContainsKey_KeyInSecondMap
test_cases.description: Tests if the CompositeMap contains a key that is present in the second map.

test_cases.name: testContainsKey_KeyNotPresent
test_cases.description: Tests if the CompositeMap does not contain a key that is not present in any map.

test_cases.name: testContainsKey_AfterAddingNewMap
test_cases.description: Tests if the CompositeMap contains a key after adding a new map to it.

test_cases.name: testContainsKey_AfterRemovingKey
test_cases.description: Tests if the CompositeMap does not contain a key after removing it.

test_cases.name: testContainsKey_AfterRemovingCompositedMap
test_cases.description: Tests if the CompositeMap does not contain a key after removing a composited map.

test_cases.name: testContainsKey_NullKey
test_cases.description: Tests if the CompositeMap does not contain a null key.

test_cases.name: testContainsKey_EmptyCompositeMap
test_cases.description: Tests if the CompositeMap does not contain a key when it is empty.
